OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Ffine and dry this evening with some
OL,7,Flate sunshine. Overnight, patchy cloud
OL,8,Fwill tend to develop with a few mist
OL,9,Fpatches also forming in prone spots.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FAnother dry and fine day
OL,12,Facross the region, with the best of
OL,13,Fthe sunny spells across the south.
OL,14,FFeeling warm once again.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FStaying fine, dry and very warm on
OL,18,FThursday and Friday. Likely to remain
OL,19,Fdry on Saturday although some rain may
OL,20,Freach the area later in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
